-- Capital Dynamics Invests $300 Million in U.S. Solar Projects
-- B y   M a r c   R o c a
-- 2012-03-15T09:58:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-15/capital-dynamics-invests-300-million-in-u-s-solar-projects.html
Capital Dynamics AG, a Swiss
private equity firm, said it invested $300 million in three
groups of solar projects in the U.S. with a combined capacity of
80 megawatts.  The company released a statment on the investments in
 California  and  New Jersey  by e-mail today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marc Roca in London at 
